{"tid":1548773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[驚黑之狗]警員截查機場巴士　旅客批評警員態度不禮貌","createTime":"2019-09-07T06:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T06:28:58.000Z","uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c0072bb789e2be028752db99fb8822c25abfc864","tid":1548773,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"有網民發起下午阻礙機場運作的行動。在青嶼幹線繳費廣場，有數十名軍裝警員截查並登上前往機場的巴士搜查及錄影，部分人被要求下車作進一步搜查，有警員亦檢查部分途經市民身份證及查問資料。<br />\n<br />\n有晚上出發往台灣的市民說，擔心交通受阻提早出門，他乘坐巴士前往機場期間，被警員要求檢查隨身物品和打開行李箱，其後被要求下車檢查，他估計是自己穿黑衣而被截查。他又說已向對方出示機票，批評警方的態度不禮貌。<br />\n<br />\n另外，有聲稱前往主題樂園的人士說，路過時被截查，警方在他身上發現雨衣及口罩時顯得較為緊張，亦檢查他的身份證，認為警方的行動擾民。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479318-20190907.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479318-20190907.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Lg84ZazuoAMv777FGbMFAcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=eed37dd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479318-20190907.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=58bf43c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479318-20190907.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\no岩勒，等狗狗對住遊客做多d柒事"},{"pid":"b3e28ea2d35af196d4624f1c78266008e0f34172","tid":1548773,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c589adcedd357e5a3766dddf72165d9811fdc5cf","tid":1548773,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:12:14.000Z","msg":"繼續做柒事啦"},{"pid":"84e152af1d5138d8296f6780a477d08e91efd745","tid":1548773,"uid":160979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:12:51.000Z","msg":"Good dog"},{"pid":"ce51b628448403d923f5742a797a945c12442fc8","tid":1548773,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"黑警繼續擾民啦"},{"pid":